commit.message: Added a few more AST checks, more readable error reporting.
Compile command now verifies contract headers properly
Fixed a parser bug with identifiers being converted to string literals. Proper string literals still aren't properly safety-checked.
Better error reporting in compile mode
Updated .gitignore
Linked an initial symbolizer pass into the compile command.
adjusting PrettyPrint util and edit example
fixed parser; created parser struct to perform parsing and hold relevent data
reorganize type definitions and change GetLine methods to have pointer receivers
expand symbol interface to AST
add environment and fix createAST cmd. gofmting and change example to include string variable
Added a function to generate errors with line numbers.
Updated makefile to closer resemble newer build system.
Fixed a dependency bug.
Cleaning up some merge conflicts
Using a newer, cleaner strategy for verifying the AST
common/util directory for commonly used util functions
gofmting and minor edits to parser and ast
use cobra/viper for command and config management
apache license
Added a function for checking type fields, fixed a minor typing issue.
A few minor tweaks - readded EmptyTable() and changed a type.
Stripped out some code in the Symbol table. We're only using strings here now.
Some formatting and minor changes
Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/i-norden/solispidy
Added a brief explanation of what the code in symbolizer.go is eventually supposed to do.
Some cleanup in symbolizer.go
Update README.md
